title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1986-06-22
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, It Must Have Been The Roses, Cassidy, Row Jimmy, Minglewood Blues-> Big Railroad Blues, Mama Tried-> Big River, Stagger Lee, Hell In A Bucket-> Might As Well

Set 2

Fire On The Mountain-> Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools-> Women Are Smarter-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Stella Blue-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: U.S. Blues, E: Box Of Rain*

*Second Encore. FM Broadcast KPFA Berkeley
